WEBVTT

00:00:57.704 --> 00:01:03.293
Maybe you feel attracted to the beauty,

00:01:03.317 --> 00:01:07.629
and while compelled by the technique,

00:01:07.653 --> 00:01:08.813
the color,

00:01:08.837 --> 00:01:10.987
the form or composition,

00:01:11.011 --> 00:01:13.503
maybe the difficult
conversation sneaks up.

00:01:13.907 --> 00:01:16.485
["Billy Lee and Ona Judge
Portraits in Tar," 2016]

00:01:16.509 --> 00:01:19.504
I really taught myself how to paint

00:01:19.528 --> 00:01:22.874
by spending time at museums

00:01:22.898 --> 00:01:26.220
and looking at the people that --

00:01:26.244 --> 00:01:30.425
the artists, rather --
that I was told were the masters.